If you move the books to Kurnak Dragons, you are punishing those Paladins who do not have access to uber guilds, huge network of friends and such.  Yes, it's ALOT easier getting the books off the Kurnak Dragons for those who are in Uber guilds, but you are punishing those Paladins who choose to stay 52nd.  <br>
