I can understand why many Paladins choose to forsake their Epic and go ahead and lvl.  The 55+ game is very different and far more exciting than the pre-52nd game.  My opinion on Alternates rolling for their main at raids is as follow. It is up to the raid leader to make that call.  Provided that Alt isn't going to roll on anything else NO MATTER what else drops.  <br>
<br>
What's wrong with a lvl 52 Paladin weilding the Epic? He/She deserved it by staying at that lvl and worked hard for it.  If you don't like the dmg on your ACGS, let me offer you a few suggestions.  Try to get some of the DN weapons, they do nice dmg and range from 30/40 to 32/36.  Or if you are a Paladin of Tunare, you should get the ND.  <br>
